<h1>Reset your password</h1>

<p>Someone requested a password reset for your account. Click the link below to reset your password:</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Reset Password", 
      identity_password_reset_url(
        password_reset_token: @signed_id,
        host: Rails.application.config.action_mailer.default_url_options[:host]
      ) 
  %>
</p>

<p>This link will expire automatically for security.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
